    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The constituent political and administrative divisions within various sovereign states, including historic ones such as the Roman Empire and modern nations under a federal system such as Canada and Spain.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
